
-------------------------------------------
|||| Git PLugin Installation ||||
-------------------------------------------


Default:
 - twister server side path: /opt/twister
 - twister client side path: /home/user/twister


	---- SERVER side ----

1. sudo cp /path/to/GitPlugin/Git /opt/twister/plugins

2. vim /path/to/twister/config/plugins.xml

append config:

<Plugin>
	<name>GIT</name>
	<jarfile>Git/GITPlugin.jar</jarfile>
	<pyfile>Git/GITPlugin.py</pyfile>
	<status>enabled</status>
	<property>
		<propname>path</propname>
		<propvalue>/home/user/test</propvalue>
	</property>
</Plugin>

